            "exposed"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "這份報告讓数千名顧客暴露在潛在的資料外洩風險中。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "The new policy exposes employees to a wider range of training opportunities.",
          "highlight": [
            "exposes"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "這項新政策讓員工有機會接觸到更廣泛的培訓機會。"
          }
        }
